{"title":"MonoGame官方文档(一)","uid":"5f6f6649742c70ec6ba94bdb691b49e4","slug":"MonoGame官方文档(一)","date":"2020-06-09T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-12-18T13:12:34.659Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/MonoGame官方文档(一).json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://images.pexels.com/photos/3046581/pexels-photo-3046581.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=750&w=1260","content":"<h1 id=\"了解代码\"><a href=\"#了解代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"了解代码\"></a><strong>了解代码</strong></h1><h1 id=\"引用包\"><a href=\"#引用包\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"引用包\"></a><strong>引用包</strong></h1><div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">using</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Microsoft</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Xna</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Framework</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">using</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Microsoft</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Xna</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Framework</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Graphics</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">using</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Microsoft</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Xna</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Framework</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Storage</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">using</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Microsoft</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Xna</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Framework</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Input</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>这些是使用MonoGame 时的一些必要的包。</p>\n<p>之所以使用Microsoft.Xna.Framework框架是，因为MonoGame是Xna的开源实现，并且为了兼容Xna使用了与之相同的命名空间。</p>\n<h1 id=\"Game1-类\"><a href=\"#Game1-类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Game1 类\"></a><strong>Game1 类</strong></h1><div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">public</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">class</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Game1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> : </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Game</span></span></code></pre></div><p>类Game1继承自Game类，Game提供了游戏框架全部的核心方法（加载&#x2F;卸载内容，刷新，绘制等）。通常情况下一个游戏只有一个Game类，所以此类的命名显得并不是那么重要。</p>\n<h1 id=\"构造器\"><a href=\"#构造器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"构造器\"></a><strong>构造器</strong></h1><div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">public</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Game1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">graphics</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> new </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GraphicsDeviceManager</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">this</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Content</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">RootDirectory</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #98C379\">&quot;Content&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>在构造函数里我们通常会初始化一些起始变量。在这里我们为我们的游戏创建了一个新的GraphicsDeviceManager（图形设备管理器），并为其设置一个了资源文件夹。</p>\n<h1 id=\"初始化方法\"><a href=\"#初始化方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初始化方法\"></a><strong>初始化方法</strong></h1><div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">protected</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">override</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">void</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Initialize</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // TODO: Add your initialization logic here</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">base</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Initialize</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">();</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>初始化方法在构造函数后游戏循环（刷新与绘制）前进行调用，在这里可以加载任何服务和非图形资源。</p>\n<h1 id=\"LoadContent方法\"><a href=\"#LoadContent方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"LoadContent方法\"></a><strong>LoadContent方法</strong></h1><div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">protected</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">override</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">void</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">LoadContent</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">()</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // Create a new SpriteBatch, which can be used to draw textures.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">spriteBatch</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">=</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> new </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">SpriteBatch</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">GraphicsDevice</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // TODO: use this.Content to load your game content here</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>此方法Initialize方法后游戏循环之前调用，用于加载我们的游戏内容，只会在每次游戏启动后调用一次。</p>\n<h1 id=\"Update方法\"><a href=\"#Update方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Update方法\"></a><strong>Update方法</strong></h1><div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">protected</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">override</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">void</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Update</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">gameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">if</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GamePad</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">GetState</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">PlayerIndex</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">One</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">).</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Buttons</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Back</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">==</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">ButtonState</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Pressed</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">||</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Keyboard</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">GetState</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">().</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">IsKeyDown</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Keys</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Escape</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">))</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">        </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Exit</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">();</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // TODO: Add your update logic here</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">base</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Update</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">gameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>每秒调用多次，并用于刷新游戏中的状态（碰撞检查，输入收集，播放音频等）。</p>\n<h1 id=\"Draw方法\"><a href=\"#Draw方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Draw方法\"></a><strong>Draw方法</strong></h1><div class=\"language-cs\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cs</span><pre class=\"shiki one-dark-pro\" style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">protected</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">override</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">void</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Draw</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">gameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">graphics</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">GraphicsDevice</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Clear</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">Color</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">CornflowerBlue</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">    // TODO: Add your drawing code here</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">    </span><span style=\"color: #E5C07B\">base</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">.</span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">Draw</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">gameTime</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span></code></pre></div><p>和Update相同也是每秒调用多次（用于绘制资源到窗口中）。</p>\n","text":"了解代码引用包csusing Microsoft.Xna.Framework; using Microsoft.Xna.Framework.Graphics; ...","permalink":"/post/MonoGame官方文档(一)","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"游戏开发","slug":"游戏开发","count":10,"path":"api/tags/游戏开发.json"},{"name":"MonoGame","slug":"MonoGame","count":4,"path":"api/tags/MonoGame.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">了解代码</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">引用包</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Game1-%E7%B1%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Game1 类</spa